src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以調轉呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係無論自己定人地都話聲好沙<br />\n<br />\n同埋手術其實只係注射物質入去<br />\n<br />\n我妹聲帶問題比我更加嚴重<br />\n<br />\n佢都做過不過做完把聲都係沙"},{"pid":"fa6d72051d2e1fb15c9d4c24106541544a2d8d2b","tid":183993,"uid":9289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:47:31.000Z","msg":"有冇話似邊個明人既聲 就咁講好難想像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416323b64f0362e158c1403bdd426930da1672fb","tid":183993,"uid":9289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:47:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇話似邊個名人既聲 就咁講好難想像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"48ef0978ade95cafca9e47b955037e8715abda4f","tid":183993,"uid":89729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:49:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇話似邊個名人既聲 就咁講好難想像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n曾志偉"},{"pid":"f3279e1f26cfb32ae64143657178b07579327c76","tid":183993,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:50:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇話似邊個名人既聲 就咁講好難想像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n曾志偉</blockquote><br />\n唔係<br />\n<br />\n唔識形容<br />\n<br />\n總之唔係女仔清脆悅耳既聲"},{"pid":"5a792c967c767b283b68e4a1401099c856687c09","tid":183993,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:50:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7df976508f865c02eb90ed4c937e7bc3c008c4c3","tid":183993,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:51:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇話似邊個名人既聲 就咁講好難想像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote>